summary: An ordinance providing for the improvement of Lakeside Avenue, South from a connection with Lake Washington Boulevard South, south of Holgate Street, to the north line of Yesler Way produced easterly, and certain parts of certain other streets and avenues, by paving and otherwise improving the same, Local Improvement District No. 5834, appropriating additional money therefor, and amending Section 1 of Ordinance No. 76921.
